<h1>What happens if I press the Stop button or refresh the page ?</h1>
<p>
	If you press the STOP button on your browser or refresh the web page,
	your current scan will continue to run in the background.
</p>
<p>
	If you refresh the web page, ScanMeNow will show you that a current
	scan is already running, and you will have to wait for that scan to
	finish before you can start another.
</p>
